<plot>Sam is a teenage boy who lives with his mother and and old man called Patrick in a pub on the River Thames. One day he sees a model aeroplane flying over the river and then a group of men hiding in an old warehouse. He watches them, and before long he discovers that they are diamond smugglers... and Patrick's son is one of the gang.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?475243</url></doc>
